    <div class="on-this-page">
      <p>Take the 'green' option and help save printing and mailing costs by opting out of receiving the Fund's general communications by post. Read them online instead.</p>
<p>When you opt out you will no longer receive:</p>
<ul>
    <li>    <a href="/pensions/news-and-publications/publications">Pensionews</a></li>
    <li><a href="/pensions/news-and-publications/publications">The Annual Review</a></li>
    <li><a href="/pensions/news-and-publications/on-the-move">On the Move</a></li>
</ul>
<p>You will still receive statements and documents that we are legally required to send if they apply to you:</p>
<ul>
    <li>    Annual payslips and P60s</li>
    <li>AVC statements</li>
    <li>Benefit statements</li>
</ul>
